Famous People with the name Gary Kovacs:







Gary Kovacs


Canadian businessman


Gary Kovacs is a San Francisco Bay Area technology innovator. He is currently the Chief Executive Officer of Mozilla Corporation. Kovacs has worked for Adobe Systems, SAP, and IBM, and co-founded Zi Corporation, a groundbreaking mobile text messaging company.






