Gary Kovacs - Chief Executive Officer & Managing Director
We're out of time.
Bonnie McBride - Vice President, Investor Relations
Right. I think we're out of time.
Operator
Yes, Bonnie?
Gary Kovacs - Chief Executive Officer & Managing Director
We're out of time.
Operator
Okay. That will conclude today's question-and-answer session. I would now like to hand the call back to Bonnie for additional or closing remarks.
Bonnie McBride - Vice President, Investor Relations
Thanks, everyone. We look forward to hopefully seeing you at a few conferences this quarter, and we'll talk to you again next quarter. Bye.
Operator
Ladies and gentlemen, that will now conclude today's conference call. We thank you for your participation, and you may now disconnect.

